annotationA: CAAX prenyl protease 2; Proteolytically removes the C-terminal three residues of farnesylated and geranylated proteins
annotationB: Ste24a prenyl protease type I (Ste24a), along with ste24b and ste24c, are paralogous (tandemly duplicated) type I prenyl proteases. Ste24a function, the most highly conserved of the three, is unknown
